name: Undercomplete
body:
# Audio Signal Coding with "Undercomplete" Basis
## Audio Gallery

### Test 1: Al Green, "Let's Stay Together"
Original
[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=COiIC3A0ROM](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=COiIC3A0ROM)

Reconstruction 1 (time-domain fit, sawtooth basis, low sparsity)
[al-uc.wav](https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/undercomplete/gallery/al-uc.wav)

Reconstruction 2 (frequency-domain fit, sawtooth basis, high sparsity)
[al-uc2.wav](https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/undercomplete/gallery/al-uc2.wav)

Reconstruction 3 (frequency-domain fit, "free jazz alto sax" basis, medium sparsity)
[al-uc2-sax.wav](https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/undercomplete/gallery/al-uc2-sax.wav)

Reconstruction 4 (frequency-domain fit, "sampled piano" basis, medium sparsity)
[al-uc2-piano-bs4.wav](https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/undercomplete/gallery/al-uc2-piano-bs4.wav)

### Test 2: Notorious B.I.G., "Big Poppa"
Original
[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=phaJXp_zMYM](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=phaJXp_zMYM)

Reconstruction (frequency-domain fit, sawtooth basis, low sparsity)
[biggy-uc2.wav](https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/undercomplete/gallery/biggy-uc2.wav)

### Test 3: R. Kelly, "Ignition (Remix)"
Original 
[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y6y_4_b6RS8](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y6y_4_b6RS8)

Reconstruction (time-domain fit, dense sawtooth basis, medium sparsity)
[ignition-uc2.wav](https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/undercomplete/gallery/ignition-uc2.wav)

### Test 4: David Bowie, "The Man Who Sold the World"
Original
[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eGoWZCOa5Qk](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eGoWZCOa5Qk)

Reconstruction (time-domain fit, dense sawtooth basis, medium sparsity)
[bowie-uc2.wav](https://ccrma.stanford.edu/~spencer/undercomplete/gallery/bowie-uc2.wav)
